                        license.
                    </TextBlock>
                    <TextBlock Foreground="#aabbc4" FontSize="13" TextWrapping="Wrap">
                        <Run Text="Source code, full license text, and everything covered in the Credits section above: " /><Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/g0fqb/hamnetprogrammer"><Run Text="github.com/g0fqb/hamnetprogrammer" /></Hyperlink>
                    </TextBlock>
                </StackPanel>
            </Border>

        </StackPanel>
    </ScrollViewer>
</Page>
